# Agent Factory Project Overview

## Project Description
Agent Factory is an autonomous development framework that enables AI agents to work together on software development tasks. The project implements a multi-agent system with specialized roles for planning, coding, testing, and deployment.

## Core Architecture

### Main Entry Points
- **CLI Interface**: [src/agent_factory/cli.py](mdc:src/agent_factory/cli.py) - Main command-line interface
- **Models**: [src/models.py](mdc:src/models.py) - Core data structures and enums
- **Base Agent**: [src/agents/base/agent_interface.py](mdc:src/agents/base/agent_interface.py) - Base class for all agents

### Agent Types
- **Planner**: [src/agents/planner/](mdc:src/agents/planner/) - Task planning and decomposition
- **Coder**: [src/agents/coder/](mdc:src/agents/coder/) - Code generation and implementation
- **Tester**: [src/agents/tester/](mdc:src/agents/tester/) - Testing and quality assurance
- **Reviewer**: [src/agents/reviewer/](mdc:src/agents/reviewer/) - Code review and validation
- **DevOps**: [src/agents/devops/](mdc:src/agents/devops/) - Deployment and infrastructure
- **Coordinator**: [src/agents/coordinator/](mdc:src/agents/coordinator/) - Agent orchestration

### Core Systems
- **Communication**: [src/communication/](mdc:src/communication/) - Inter-agent messaging and protocols
- **Knowledge**: [src/knowledge/](mdc:src/knowledge/) - Memory, RAG, and vector storage
- **Workflows**: [src/workflows/](mdc:src/workflows/) - Process orchestration and monitoring
- **API**: [src/api/](mdc:src/api/) - REST and streaming interfaces
- **Tools**: [src/tools/](mdc:src/tools/) - Utility functions and integrations

## Configuration
- **Settings**: [src/config/settings.py](mdc:src/config/settings.py) - Application configuration and environment variables
- **Project Config**: [pyproject.toml](mdc:pyproject.toml) - Python project configuration and dependencies

## Development Workflow
- **PRPs**: [PRPs/](mdc:PRPs/) - Product Requirement Prompts for task definition
- **Scripts**: [scripts/](mdc:scripts/) - Development and deployment utilities
- **Tests**: [tests/](mdc:tests/) - Test suite and validation

## Key Concepts
- **Agent Interface**: All agents inherit from BaseAgent for consistent behavior
- **Message Bus**: Redis-based pub/sub for inter-agent communication
- **Vector Store**: Chroma-based knowledge storage and retrieval
- **Execution Results**: Structured response objects for consistent agent outputs
- **Task Management**: Hierarchical task decomposition and execution tracking
